@Node 21 "Configuration"
What Is In The Configuration File?
----------------------------------

The configuration file is back!  It goes in your MEBBSNET:CONFIGFILES/
directory.

---cut here

Larry Cloud
sys:bin/zip
sys:bin/lha
sys:bin/uuxt
1
1
1
1
1

-----------

The above entries correspond to:

Line  Desc
----  ----

1     Sysop Name
2     Path to ZIP (put RAM: if you don't want to use ZIP)
3     Path to LHA (put RAM: if you don't want to use LHA)
4     Path to UUXT (put RAM: if you don't want to use UUE)
5     1 if you have/want to use ZIP, 0 if not
6     1 if you have/want to use LHA, 0 if not
7     1 if you have/want to use UUE, 0 if not
8     Number corresponding to your number format (SEE BELOW, USA=1)
9     Message Area # for E-Mail

NF.1 ="XXX-XXX-XXXX"     /* USA, Canada, New Zealand, Taiwan, Guam */
NF.2 ="XXX-XXXX-XXXX"    /* UK */
NF.3 ="XXXX-XXXXX"       /* UK */
